{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog05/10/recipe/spaghetti/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://dannypsnl.github.io"}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3>材料</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>筆管麵</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://24h.pchome.com.tw/prod/DBAK0Z-A9005Y8J4\">奶油塊</a></li>\n<li>牛奶 50ml</li>\n<li>鹽</li>\n<li>開水</li>\n<li>沙拉油</li>\n<li>洋蔥</li>\n<li>蒜</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>可選</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>培根</li>\n<li>蘑菇</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>流程</h3>\n<h4>1. 備料</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>切蒜碎</li>\n<li>切洋蔥絲</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>2-1. 麵</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>開水煮沸後加入 2 匙鹽(或是罐裝轉 6 次)</li>\n<li>計時 12 分鐘，放入筆管麵，時間到關火</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>2-2. 白醬(煮麵時間約剩 6 分時開始做)</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>沙拉油放入鍋子熱油，大火</li>\n<li>(optional) 放入培根跟蘑菇後炒 30 秒</li>\n<li>放入洋蔥絲跟蒜碎後炒 30 秒後轉中小火</li>\n<li>放入 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\frac{1}{4}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.190108em;vertical-align:-0.345em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.845108em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.6550000000000002em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">4</span></span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.394em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.345em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span></span></span></span> 奶油塊</li>\n<li>放入熱水 100ml(從隔壁煮麵的鍋子撈)</li>\n<li>放入牛奶，等收汁就好了</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>3. 混合</h4>\n<p>最後把麵倒進白醬裡，就完成了</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"奶油白醬義大利麵","categories":["recipe"],"tags":["spaghetti","white sauce"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog05/10/recipe/spaghetti/"}}}